¶ With Gilligan ¶

00:46.179 --> 00:48.413
¶ The Skipper too ¶

00:48.482 --> 00:50.815
¶ The millionaire ¶

00:50.884 --> 00:53.018
¶ And his wife ¶

00:53.087 --> 00:55.921
¶ The movie star ¶

